name: Left Over Papers no. 1
description:
3D Model of Paper Scraps.

Analog collage making always left scraps behind. I keep those scraps thinking that they will be useful in the future, sometimes I also give them to my partner for her own collage making.

I scanned those scraps and with Blender I started to turn them into a series of 3D compositions. The composition of those unglued scraps becomes a collage by itself. This exploration with 3D format provides me with even more possibilities in collage making for my own progress as an artist.

You can see my collages on feransis.com or instagram (@tuhanzilla).
